Q: What are important notes for sevas at Srisailam?
A: Timings for sevas may vary on festival days. Advance booking is strongly recommended especially during Maha Shivaratri, Karthika Masam and Navratri. All sevas can be booked online at srisailadevasthanam.org. Strict dress code applies ‚Äî traditional Indian attire mandatory. High rush is expected during major festivals so plan accordingly.ˇˇˇˇˇ